;W[oq]LB[ss:1][sq:2][ps:3][sp:4][oq:5]C[Dia.2 Living in matbogi

White will of course capture with 1.  Black takes away an eye with 2, then White takes 3.  When Black connects at 4, White takes, and now we see that it is matbogi for White to live.
\lang1042\f1\fs18



















