;B[rs]LB[sq:1][sr:2][rs:3][sp:B][ss:A]C[Dia.3 Correct / Black 1

When Black plays 1 he has succeeded in taking White out.  When White blocks at 2 THEN we play the throw in of 3.  If White takes at A he'll get captured in snapback, and if White plays at B then Black will just capture the seven White stones on the side by taking.
\lang1042\f1\fs18

